Enjoy the most spectacular Barossa Valley views to be seen from your own private deck, lounge and both guest bedrooms.
You might even see my four-legged friends, Hercules and Twiggy, wandering around their paddock or begging for carrots!
This is the view that never gets old! Sit on the deck,  sip a glass of Barossa Shiraz, graze on a Barossa Cheese Co. platter and watch the seasons change over the Barossa Valley.

You'll feel at home and relaxed the minute you step out of the car and walk through the landscaped gardens to the front door. I'll be there to greet you and show you around the property, then available if you need me at any time.
Main guest suite. Super soft king sized bed with large wardrobe. Relax and enjoy beautiful views over the Barossa Valley while you sit in bed sipping your morning coffee.
Enjoy a glass of wine while watching the sunset from your own deck area. The views from here are some of the very best the Barossa Valley has to offer.

Guest's private lounge and deck area. All enjoying the spectacular Barossa Valley views. 
Private access to the house through here via the garage which is also made available for guests to use.
Sunrises are also spectacular from here on the hill, overlooking the Barossa Valley.

This second queen sized guest bedroom is also available for your stay if travelling with another couple.
Relax and soak up the same gorgeous Barossa Valley views as suite one, a large built in wardrobe and plenty of room to move.

Take a stroll around the stunning landscaped gardens that surround the house. Plants have been chosen specifically for their waterwise nature and hilltop living. Everything has been carefully chosen to complement the views over the Valley.

The kitchen and main living area are shared spaces, you are always welcome to join me in front of the fire for a quiet night in.
Why would you cook when the Barossa has so much to offer though? If you do wish to, please make a request before booking.

This shared main living and dining space with combustion fire leads off the kitchen. Large sliding glass doors open up to the shared deck overlooking the Barossa Valley with spectacular sunsets. A BBQ is available for use out on this deck.
Sunset views from the deck, what better way to welcome the evening in than a glass of wine watching the sun go down over the Valley?
Most Barossa winter mornings you'll see both hot air balloons drifting over the Valley while the sun comes up.

The 7km long Angaston-Nuriootpa dedicated walking/cycling track starts less than 1km from the house. This leads past the stunning recently renovated railway precinct, mountain bike track and nature play park.

Walk less than 1km to Angaston for restaurants, cafes, Barossa Cheese Company, Casa Carboni Italian Cooking School and all other town attractions. The property is unique in that it enjoys being right near town yet a world away all at the same time.

Apartmán 4 je situován v přízemí penzionu a je zde možné ubytovat až 5 osob. Ubytování se skládá ze světnice s kuchyňským koutem a krbem, dále je zde ložnice a koupelna se záchodem. Jsou k dispozici 3 lůžka a rozkládací pohovka pro 2 osoby.

Náš penzion je citlivě zrenovovaný dům v srdci České Kanady. Nachází se zde čtyři apartmány, venkovní posezení, velká zahrada, ovocný sad  a ovečky. Je možné si pronajmout celou chalupu nebo jednotlivé apartmány. Kapacita celého penzionu je 23 hostů.
Kuchyň je plně vybavená a najdete zde varnou desku, mikrovlnku, rychlovarnou konvici, ledničku a základní koření. Topíme v krbu.
Ubytování zahrnuje televizi se satelitem a wifi.

Apartmán byl citlivě zrekonstruován s přihlédnutím na původní rustikální prvky. Byly použity kvalitní materiály jako je masivní dřevo a kamenné prvky na krbu. Pokud hledáte atmosféru starého selského stavení, pak je toto ubytování pro Vás to pravé.
V ložnici najdete pohodlnou manželskou postel (180 x 200) a samostatné lůžko. V ceně jsou povlečení a ručníky.
Ložnice je orientovaná na sever a byly zde zachovány staré klenby.
V koupelně najdete sprchový kout, umyvadlo a záchod. Okno do dvora je možné zastínit roletou. V koupelně je elektrické podlahové topení.
Do penzionu se vstupuje přes tuto útulnou dřevěnou verandu.
Z verandy se jde do společné chodby s klenutými stropy a kamenným schodištěm.
V chodbě se zachovaly původní kamenné schody a kamenné překlady dveří. Dále je zde dnes již nefunkční pumpa na vodu.
Nabízíme jedinečnou dovolenou v rustikálním stylu.
